Description:
Cabela's African Adventures - hunting simulator in a completely open world where the player has the opportunity to go to Africa and meet with representatives of the most bloodthirsty animals. In this part of the virtual world is more than five times higher than what has been realized in previous games Cabela's for consoles. In this case, there is a possibility at any time to use trucks to move quickly . In Cabela's African Adventures presents two modes - Safari , where the player must perform a number of tasks , and Tyre, with the support of game accessories Top Shot Elite and Top Shot Fearmaster.
